Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.20,0:06:31.75,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)\pos(100,360)\shad1\4c&HF7F4F2&}敲\N不\N倒\N翁
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.02,0:07:24.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那开始了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.58,0:07:26.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,石头 剪子 布
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.09,0:07:40.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不对啊 麻衣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.35,0:07:41.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才不是说明过了么！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.00,0:07:43.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赢了的话就要敲对方啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.62,0:07:45.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好狠哦！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.54,0:07:46.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好狠的做法哦！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.07,0:07:48.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从另一个层面说比敲我更过分哦！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.47,0:07:51.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说好了哦 就像刚才说明的那样
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.00,0:07:54.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,输了的话就要防御 赢了的话就要敲对方哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.37,0:07:56.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs70\c&H86F8FB&\3c&H000000&\bord2\shad0\b1\frz353.178\pos(1167,185)}猛击
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.30,0:07:59.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在打你妹啊！ 为毛现在打我！？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.16,0:08:01.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是 刚才不是赢了么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.81,0:08:03.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是现在 是刚才！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.52,0:08:06.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就那个瞬间哦 就那个瞬间生效哦！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.01,0:08:09.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们就是那种生物哦！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.25,0:08:22.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 接下来
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.37,0:08:23.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,清零重新开始哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.01,0:08:25.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,石头 剪刀 布
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.13,0:08:27.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干劲是零啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.40,0:08:30.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小丑啊 没想到是个小丑啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.27,0:08:34.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,精神上的打击 也是有的啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.37,0:08:38.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 我说 麻衣
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.71,0:08:41.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.73,0:08:47.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻衣 那个 怎么回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.93,0:08:48.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雕了一个
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.17,0:08:52.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了 我还以为重生过来了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.74,0:08:54.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把这个 放这里
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.01,0:08:59.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感觉 她好像非常高兴啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.99,0:09:03.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 那种东西怎么样都可以啦 继续吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.79,0:09:08.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来 石头 剪刀 布
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.34,0:09:10.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻 麻衣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.60,0:09:12.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.50,0:09:14.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是石剪布嘛！！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.70,0:09:14.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs70\3c&H000000&\bord2\shad0\b1\pos(1201,221)\c&H8CF4F6&}暴击!!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.97,0:09:18.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么… 这么残忍
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.62,0:09:21.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 麻衣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.54,0:09:23.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不带的哦 不带的 不带石剪布的！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.79,0:09:25.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后也不带用佛像敲的！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.92,0:09:29.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那 来了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.75,0:09:31.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先出石头
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.76,0:09:33.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,石头 剪刀 布
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.52,0:09:50.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻衣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.48,0:09:53.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了对了 就是这样哦麻衣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.15,0:09:56.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊真是的 你这不是也可以嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.86,0:09:58.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 继续了哦 继续
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.82,0:10:01.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个 先出 石…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.74,0:10:01.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fs33}Gascoigne貌似是人名，加斯科因
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.08,0:10:05.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,GOD IS DEAD
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.29,0:10:07.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神 死了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.59,0:10:12.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说 为什么打我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.71,0:10:15.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 刚才玩的不是好好的么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.30,0:10:18.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么说呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.39,0:10:20.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为不想玩
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.31,0:10:29.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弥勒菩萨 可以借我看看么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.23,0:10:30.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.78,0:10:43.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那 我去图书馆还书去了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.95,0:10:48.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要好好看家哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.62,0:10:49.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好~
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.67,0:10:57.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\shad0\bord0\fs24\c&H525351&\pos(135,594)}雪糕\N果汁\N不能吃\N太多哦！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.84,0:10:58.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord0\shad0\fs24\c&HB8ECE0&\pos(1073,623)}鲨鱼型的巧克力\N为什么这么好吃！！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.55,0:11:03.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么名乃的不倒翁只有一个眼睛呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.97,0:11:08.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对啦 博士把眼睛好好画上去的话 说不定会被夸奖
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.81,0:11:13.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说不定 名乃会说吃好多点心也可以哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.00,0:11:33.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像有点弄错了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.21,0:11:36.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明是名乃的 怎么办啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.72,0:11:40.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说不定 会被骂…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.57,0:11:42.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}博士暂时不许吃点心！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.16,0:11:48.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃 这样 这样…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.82,0:11:54.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.03,0:11:58.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阪本 怎么办啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.24,0:11:59.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.45,0:12:00.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么啊这是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.49,0:12:01.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你做什么了啊！？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.32,0:12:03.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个 是那小姑娘的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.12,0:12:07.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为 没有眼睛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.80,0:12:16.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有办法呐
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.67,0:12:18.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,按照我说的办吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.23,0:12:32.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.02,0:12:34.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你保重哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.14,0:12:37.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阪本！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.49,0:12:40.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊咧 阪本先生你要出去么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.66,0:12:42.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,博士 我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.07,0:12:46.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要选新借的书 所以回来晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.37,0:12:48.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.04,0:12:52.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说 博士 怎么回事啊 你的肚子！？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.46,0:12:55.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶嘿 嘿嘿嘿嘿嘿 诶嘿
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.25,0:12:56.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不是“诶嘿嘿”
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.26,0:13:01.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我 我要生了！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.76,0:13:05.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不对不对不对 不可能这么回事吧！？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.81,0:13:07.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就是要生了！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.31,0:13:10.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs45}我要生了！我要生了！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.51,0:13:10.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个… 啊 是什么游戏么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.60,0:13:13.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不是呢 名乃的弟弟要生出来了！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.12,0:13:35.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是你的弟弟
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.21,0:13:40.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行啊 这样
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.76,0:14:30.01,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,0)\pos(750,360)\shad1\4c&HF7F4F2&}狐\N狗\N狸\N先\N生
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.55,0:14:29.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美绪 美绪
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.97,0:14:30.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.27,0:14:32.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们来玩“狐狗狸先生”吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.81,0:14:34.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃 那是什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.89,0:14:36.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇 美绪你竟然不知道啊！？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.06,0:14:38.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唔知…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.15,0:14:40.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就 稍微给你说明一下哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.15,0:14:44.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首先 准备一张像这样 在正中间画一个鸟居
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.15,0:14:44.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs36}鸟居：神社入口的牌坊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.57,0:14:48.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,写着“是”和“不是”还有五十音图的纸哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.45,0:14:48.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.24,0:14:55.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不同的地方也有给神画上油炸豆腐比较好的说法
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.24,0:14:55.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs36\an8}译注：日本人普遍认为狐狸爱吃油炸豆腐
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.04,0:14:58.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在就只画最简单的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.79,0:14:59.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.50,0:15:02.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后 为了让狐狗狸先生能够进来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.25,0:15:04.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把北边的窗子开启
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.63,0:15:05.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.38,0:15:09.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后 把这个十元硬币 放在这个鸟居的位置
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.35,0:15:12.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两个人一起把手指放上面
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.35,0:15:14.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,提问想问的问题
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.27,0:15:18.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别人的秘密 喜欢的人的事情 烦恼的事情之类的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.77,0:15:19.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.56,0:15:21.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样的话 明明什么都没做
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.65,0:15:25.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,十元硬币却自己来回动 狐狗狸先生会回答你的问题哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.95,0:15:26.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶～
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.15,0:15:28.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐 很厉害吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.66,0:15:30.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 有几条禁止事项
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.70,0:15:32.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首先 不能自己一个人玩
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.12,0:15:34.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有 不能开玩笑的玩
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.70,0:15:36.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为会被低级妖怪盯上的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.16,0:15:37.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.96,0:15:41.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有 中途停止的话也会被盯上的 一定要注意
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.21,0:15:43.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.50,0:15:46.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是这个感觉 还是一个挺有危险的游戏哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.72,0:15:48.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之 我们来玩玩试试吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.80,0:15:49.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还是算了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.09,0:15:52.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊～咧～
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.90,0:16:09.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个 那么今天就这样结束吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.16,0:16:14.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天要进行小测验 大家要好好学习哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.37,0:16:16.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶 延期吧 延期吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.04,0:16:19.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你丫不管怎么延期结果都一样吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.46,0:16:24.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs36\bord0\shad0\c&HE5FBE2&\pos(265,545)}小\N测\N验
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.83,0:16:22.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,估计吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.88,0:16:24.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,樱井老师
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.34,0:16:27.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相生同学 怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.30,0:16:29.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有点事想问…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.63,0:16:30.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.59,0:16:34.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是关于之前做的那个测试的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.60,0:16:36.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个 是什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.64,0:16:38.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个 那个是FLY哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.69,0:16:41.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 不是 不是想问答案
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.52,0:16:43.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个好像会被抹杀光线消灭的小怪
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.52,0:16:43.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs33\fnＤＦブラッシュＲＤW7}ニフラム{\r\fs36}：勇者斗恶龙中用光束抹杀敌人的魔法
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.19,0:16:44.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是老师你画的么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.27,0:16:46.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 是的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.73,0:16:50.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得如果放点画上去的话 考试会变得温柔一些之类的…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.90,0:16:53.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师画的画很有意思哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.82,0:16:54.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.95,0:16:58.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我画画很差的 很难理解吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.91,0:17:00.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 对了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.42,0:17:05.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那老师 下一次把我画的画放上去吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.63,0:17:07.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会画一些超帅的画的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.59,0:17:08.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.80,0:17:10.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 美绪
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.72,0:17:13.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快听 快听 我画的话要放到考试里面去哦！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.93,0:17:15.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶 为什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.35,0:17:17.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师说会给我放进去
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.93,0:17:20.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美绪现在也开始画的画 说不定会全都放上去哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.06,0:17:23.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽说是全都放上去还是会漏一些的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.40,0:17:25.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊咧 你不画么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.02,0:17:28.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 我就算了吧 不用了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.78,0:17:30.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我得赶紧把这个还回去
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.53,0:17:31.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 是么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.90,0:17:35.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的 那我来画一笔帅哥！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.00,0:17:45.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种感觉的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.92,0:17:49.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇 好帅哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.67,0:17:53.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相生同学画画真好哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.84,0:17:54.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,令人敬仰啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.05,0:18:00.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀 我啊 厉害吧 什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.35,0:18:04.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,顺便一提名字就叫做“五月雨乔治”
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.90,0:18:07.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呜啊 更加更加帅了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.90,0:18:10.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帅！？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.95,0:18:17.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍微等一下 二位
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.66,0:18:19.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一般说的帅…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.50,0:18:24.00,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24\bord0\shad0\frz21\pos(408,413)\c&H767378&}忧\N郁
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.62,0:18:23.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该是这样吧！？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.41,0:18:25.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呜啊 好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.96,0:18:27.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像漫画一样
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.92,0:18:30.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,长野原同学 你有在画漫画什么的么？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.30,0:18:32.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 没有 就一点点而已
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.26,0:18:35.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厉害 下次请给我看看哟
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.84,0:18:37.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 那可有点…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.80,0:18:39.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？ 不可以么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.60,0:18:41.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好想看 请给我看看吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.64,0:18:43.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶 啊 但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.73,0:18:46.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍微借我一下！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.73,0:18:49.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的会更帅的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.19,0:18:53.69,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs27\bord0\shad0\c&H767378&\frz324.472\pos(442,255)}忧\N\N郁
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.04,0:18:55.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不就是抄袭么！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.82,0:18:56.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有抄袭哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.03,0:18:58.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是抄袭哦！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.57,0:19:00.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名叫抄袭的致敬哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.78,0:19:02.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,承认了啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.62,0:19:04.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇 好帅哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.62,0:19:06.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么样的都可以吗？！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.17,0:19:17.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那 这样的怎么样？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.26,0:19:19.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,眼镜！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.18,0:19:23.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又知性又酷的形象到哪个时代都是女性的憧憬对象！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.39,0:19:28.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 眼镜哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.52,0:19:31.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,眼睛不太好么？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.19,0:19:34.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戴隐形眼镜不就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.44,0:19:37.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这群人完全不能理解我！！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.53,0:19:39.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我的就…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.24,0:19:40.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个样子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.87,0:19:42.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,架在耳朵下面了！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.74,0:19:44.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说你这也是抄袭吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.95,0:19:46.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是太阳镜
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.08,0:19:48.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇 好帅~
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.83,0:19:50.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差别对待啊！！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.79,0:19:52.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那 这样子如何！？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.46,0:19:53.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,管家！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.21,0:19:56.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从迎接到泡红茶 已经让人有千金小姐的感觉了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.42,0:19:58.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接受大吉岭的魔力吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.42,0:19:58.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs36}大吉岭：指大吉岭红茶 印度大吉岭地区产的红茶 被誉为“茶中香槟”
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.88,0:20:00.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃 啊 还是眼镜？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.54,0:20:02.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思 我看不太懂这种
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.68,0:20:05.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不听隐形眼镜的忠告
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.73,0:20:11.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美绪你不能理解啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.98,0:20:15.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说啊 真正的帅气这个东西是啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.35,0:20:19.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这种东西
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.66,0:20:21.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,浮着呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.99,0:20:23.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不对 给我等等 这货…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.83,0:20:25.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跑着呢么！！？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.58,0:20:28.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看起来很快 好帅啊~
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.66,0:20:30.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太扯了——
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.13,0:20:33.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帅气这种东西是…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.21,0:20:35.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帅气这种东西是…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.46,0:20:38.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帅气这种东西是…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.17,0:20:43.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,符合常识… 符合常识的考虑
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.39,0:20:46.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帅气这种东西是——
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.77,0:20:51.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种东西吧！！！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.61,0:21:05.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完蛋啦……
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.91,0:21:07.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开玩笑啦～
